Package: MonocleScripts
Title: Command line scripts for Monocle3
Version: 0.0.5
Authors@R: c(
    person('Ni', 'Huang', email='nh3@users.noreply.github.com', role=c('aut', 'cre')),
    person('Krzysztof', 'Polanski', email='ktpolanski@users.noreply.github.com', role='aut'))
Description: This package provides a set of command line wrapper scripts for
    Monocle3 functions to facilitate building flexible workflows using different
    frameworks.
